main event: A flying object was observed by military personnel at Olmsted AFB, Pennsylvania, possibly identified as a mirage or goose.
interesting points: The sighting was recorded in a Project Blue Book document., The object was described as a circular or disc-shaped UFO., Observers indicated the object showed tremendous horizontal speed., There were sketches included to illustrate the observed object's movement., The object appeared to handle rapidly and disappeared from view instantaneously.
sighted object: circular or disc-shaped unidentified flying object
witness description: Military personnel and observers involved in the report
